title: [BBC] Cambridge spies.2003 / mini series ALL FILES
description:
CAMBRIDGE SPIES. BBC 2003.

Cambridge Spies was a 2003 four-part BBC television drama concerning the lives of the Cambridge Five from 1934 to the defection of Guy Burgess and Donald Maclean to the Soviet Union. It was written by Peter Moffat and directed by Tim Fywell.
(http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Cambridge_Spies)

    * Guy Burgess - Tom Hollander
    * Kim Philby - Toby Stephens
    * Anthony Blunt - Samuel West
    * Donald Maclean - Rupert Penry-Jones
